title: WT_NDF_1
characteristics_ch1: diet: normal chow
treatment_protocol_ch1: WT and Cyp2b-null mice were fed either a normal chow diet (ND) or choline-deficient, L-amino acid-defined high fat diet (CDAHFD, 0.1% methionine and 62% fat) for 8 weeks.
extract_protocol_ch1: Livers were removed and stored at -80 degrees C. RNA was extracted from each treatment group (n=4) using Trizol.
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Libraries were prepared using NEB Next Ultra RNA Library Prep kit.
data_processing: Illumina Control Software/Real-Time Analysis (RTA) was used for base-calling.
data_processing.1: Samples were sequenced to an average sequencing depth of 20,000,000 read pairs with a 2 x 150 paired-end module.
data_processing.2: Quality metrics were checked using FastQC on all samples sequenced, and Trimmomatic was used to trim low quality bases.
data_processing.3: Trimmed reads were aligned to the Mus musculus reference genome (GCF_000001635.25_GRCm38.p6) using GSNAP.  Subread feature counts software finds reads that aligned with known genes.
data_processing.4: Raw read counts and EdgeR were used to determine differential gene expression.
data_processing.6: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: Tab-deliminated text file includes raw counts for each sample.

extract_protocol_ch1: Livers were removed and stored at -80 degrees C. RNA was extracted from each treatment group (n=4) using Trizol.
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Libraries were prepared using NEB Next Ultra RNA Library Prep kit.
data_processing: Illumina Control Software/Real-Time Analysis (RTA) was used for base-calling.
data_processing.1: Samples were sequenced to an average sequencing depth of 20,000,000 read pairs with a 2 x 150 paired-end module.
data_processing.2: Quality metrics were checked using FastQC on all samples sequenced, and Trimmomatic was used to trim low quality bases.
data_processing.3: Trimmed reads were aligned to the Mus musculus reference genome (GCF_000001635.25_GRCm38.p6) using GSNAP.  Subread feature counts software finds reads that aligned with known genes.
data_processing.4: Raw read counts and EdgeR were used to determine differential gene expression.
data_processing.6: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: Tab-deliminated text file includes raw counts for each sample.
